boonga
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a Polynesian, usu. a Pacific Islander, less freq. a Maori [an elaboration of <i>boong</i>;


Origin: [none]
Register: offensive

Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See: also bong, boong
Pronunciation:
